The invention, together with additional objects, features and advantages thereof, will be best understood from the following description, the appended claims and the accompanying drawings in which:


FIG. 1 is a block diagram that illustrates a power distribution system in accordance with a presently preferred implementation of the invention;


FIG. 2 is a perspective view of a load shed module in accordance with a presently preferred embodiment of the invention;


FIG. 3 is a functional block diagram of the load shed module of FIG. 2 in the power distribution system of FIG. 1;


FIGS. 4A, 4B, 4C and 4D together comprise an electrical schematic diagram of the load shed module illustrated in FIGS. 2 and 3;


FIG. 5 is a state diagram useful in describing operation of the load shed module; and


FIG. 6 is a functional block diagram that illustrates the technique for calibrating the load shed module in accordance with the invention.
